# Change Log

All notable changes to brdkViBase will be documented in this file.
The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](http://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/)
and brdkViBase adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Released]
## [1.00.4] - 2022-11-21
### Added
- Detailed documentation

## [1.00.3] - 2022-11-15
### Added
- Added many data structures to ease binding to hardware, camera, lights and vision functions

### Changed
- Added support for brdkViBase_imgTrigger to support simulation

### Fixed
- brdkViBase_imgTrigger: Fixed bug with not triggering correctly

## [1.00.2] - 2022-10-13
### Fixed
- Formated enties in changelog

## [1.00.1] - 2022-10-12
### Added
- All needed hardware stuctures for both camera, lights and vision function
- Function block to simplify image triggering

## [1.00.0] - 2022-1-7
### Added
- Initial released version
